BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 5: Sleep Hygiene Protocol) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (The Ideal Evening Routine) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 652.2 Td (3 Hours Before Bed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 636.2 Td (- Finish last meal) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 622.2 Td (- No more caffeine \(ideally none after noon\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 608.2 Td (- Complete any vigorous exercise) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 590.2 Td (2 Hours Before Bed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 574.2 Td (- Dim lights throughout the house) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 560.2 Td (- Begin winding down activities) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 546.2 Td (- Avoid intense conversations or work) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 528.2 Td (1 Hour Before Bed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 512.2 Td (- All screens OFF \(blue light blocks melatonin\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 498.2 Td (- Take a warm bath or shower \(body cooling triggers sleep\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 484.2 Td (- Relaxation practice: reading, gentle stretching, meditation) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 466.2 Td (30 Minutes Before Bed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 450.2 Td (- Prepare bedroom: cool \(60-67F\), dark, quiet) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 436.2 Td (- Journaling or brain dump \(write worries on paper\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 422.2 Td (- Gentle breathing or progressive muscle relaxation) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 392.4 Td (Bedroom Environment Optimization) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 374.4 Td (- Temperature: 60-67 degrees Fahrenheit \(15-19 Celsius\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 360.4 Td (- Darkness: Blackout curtains, cover all LED lights) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 346.4 Td (- Sound: White noise machine or earplugs if needed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 332.4 Td (- Remove clutter and work materials from bedroom) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 318.4 Td (- Comfortable mattress and pillows \(replace every 7-10 years\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 304.4 Td (- Reserve bed for sleep and intimacy only) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 274.6 Td (Morning Routine for Better Sleep) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 256.6 Td (- Wake at the same time every day \(even weekends\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 242.6 Td (- Get bright light within 30 minutes of waking) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 228.6 Td (- Move your body \(even a short walk\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 214.6 Td (- Avoid hitting snooze \(fragments sleep\)) Tj ET
endstream
