BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 6: Nutrition, Exercise & Supplements) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Foods That Promote Sleep) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (- Tart cherry juice \(natural melatonin source\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (- Kiwi fruit \(shown to improve sleep onset\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.2 Td (- Almonds and walnuts \(melatonin and magnesium\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.2 Td (- Turkey \(tryptophan\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 600.2 Td (- Chamomile tea \(apigenin promotes relaxation\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 586.2 Td (- Fatty fish \(omega-3s and vitamin D\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 572.2 Td (- Warm milk \(tryptophan and psychological comfort\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 542.4 Td (Foods That Disrupt Sleep) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 524.4 Td (- Caffeine \(half-life 5-6 hours, affects sleep even if you fall asleep\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 510.4 Td (- Alcohol \(disrupts REM sleep and causes awakenings\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 496.4 Td (- Spicy foods \(raise body temperature\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 482.4 Td (- High-sugar foods \(blood sugar crashes\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 468.4 Td (- Heavy meals close to bedtime) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 438.6 Td (Exercise and Sleep) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 420.6 Td (- Regular exercise improves sleep quality significantly) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 406.6 Td (- 30 minutes of moderate exercise most days) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 392.6 Td (- Complete vigorous exercise 3+ hours before bed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 378.6 Td (- Morning or afternoon exercise is ideal for sleep) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 364.6 Td (- Yoga and stretching in the evening can help relaxation) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 334.8 Td (Supplements to Discuss with Your Doctor) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 316.8 Td (- Magnesium glycinate: 200-400mg before bed \(calming\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 302.8 Td (- Melatonin: 0.5-3mg \(for circadian issues, not long-term\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 288.8 Td (- L-theanine: 200mg \(promotes relaxation without drowsiness\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 274.8 Td (- Glycine: 3g before bed \(lowers core body temperature\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 260.8 Td (- Valerian root: May improve sleep quality) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 246.8 Td (- Ashwagandha: Reduces cortisol, improves sleep) Tj ET
