endobj
102 0 obj
<< /Length 276 >>
stream
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 720.0 Td (Absolutely. Anxiety and insomnia form a bidirectional cycle - each worsens the other.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 706.0 Td (CBT-I addresses both by reducing hyperarousal and breaking the anxiety-insomnia) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 692.0 Td (connection.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
